{"tid":221303,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"擺低心事 同我傾下計 做樹洞","createTime":"2017-04-28T15:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T15:22:22.000Z","uid":93964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f6bd0ad40ceefab7936b3bd84e21de57850fc19","tid":221303,"uid":93964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n同條女一齊咗2年 呢兩年都無咩特別 <br />\n其實佢都幾好 係我驚比佢睇唔起 <br />\n所以出街咩洗費都唔會要佢比錢 <br />\n佢同我性格唔到 我好多野講 但係佢就好靜 <br />\n做咗佢隻兵2年先同到佢一齊<br />\n本來...我應該好珍惜呢段關係<br />\n<br />\n我幾乎將我全部時間比曬佢  有時真係想去挽下  <br />\n可惜 唔知點解我身邊所有既朋友佢都唔鍾意<br />\n我開始覺得好攰 好想放棄呢段關係...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵人理下我 比返啲存在感我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f46dd8ec8a09110fc4da04e818beafa25f6a47","tid":221303,"uid":83601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:16:00.000Z","msg":"因咩事 唔鍾意你d朋友先"},{"pid":"360cac9b22e0261ddfb4cea5f6191dba463f9704","tid":221303,"uid":93964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因咩事 唔鍾意你d朋友先</blockquote><br />\n無原因 永遠會話 總之我好憎佢"},{"pid":"6227b521dd1684a988ef1f705703e07b560b4336","tid":221303,"uid":83601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因咩事 唔鍾意你d朋友先</blockquote><br />\n無原因 永遠會話 總之我好憎佢</blockquote><br />\n所以你想分手？"},{"pid":"fac4d00e91e0028e7d703b5a559ccf1f6b2f3018","tid":221303,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"女人永遠都係好撚自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5b6a0502ef7a45ef69799a27f88912a996674e","tid":221303,"uid":93964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因咩事 唔鍾意你d朋友先</blockquote><br />\n無原因 永遠會話 總之我好憎佢</blockquote><br />\n所以你想分手？</blockquote><br />\n唔係一個，佢唯一一個唔敢憎就係我個兄弟，佢知我一憎就會同佢反面 <br />\n當然唔想 但日日問自己 咁辛苦為咩 佢可以因為小小野嬲 我不停氹佢 佢只係會得寸進尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}